paternity leave is actually

00:49:30.960 --> 00:49:32.380
a big feminist issue.

00:49:32.380 --> 00:49:34.400
I think that's really
important, too.

00:49:34.400 --> 00:49:36.630
And so for me,
what really helped

00:49:36.630 --> 00:49:41.370
me was all the great support
and mentors that I had.

00:49:41.370 --> 00:49:42.750
It's hard.

00:49:42.750 --> 00:49:44.220
Any job is hard.

00:49:44.220 --> 00:49:50.230
