feel a lot more pressure.

00:49:53.510 --> 00:49:56.630
And I guess I'm here
to say, there's so much

00:49:56.630 --> 00:49:58.220
support out there for you.

00:49:58.220 --> 00:49:59.610
Don't be afraid to ask.

00:49:59.610 --> 00:50:02.550
Don't feel like you
have to go it alone.

00:50:02.550 --> 00:50:05.400
